{"tid":565423,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[SSD] 想買隻500GB SSD MX300定MX500好","createTime":"2018-02-19T03:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T08:02:17.000Z","uid":88689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"567683198459dc0d89750c5c1e2dd71e0a1acf7c","tid":565423,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"其實都係諗住俾PS4 Pro用<br />\n但遲啲可能拆返出黎俾PC<br />\nBudget $1000左右 最好唔過$1100<br />\n<br />\n如果唔貪多25GB<br />\n係咪揀MX500最理想<br />\n定各位師父有其他推薦？"},{"pid":"c81476c1675d2cb626523d3e17b8dc847629a656","tid":565423,"uid":166675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"筆直得1100根本無得揀"},{"pid":"35e3d3f720e0e68464f982b97274332613db91a5","tid":565423,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"我見台仔推545s ms2259<br />\n香港係咪冇賣呢隻"},{"pid":"8be80d5b5edb5d964b87f99b4ff6ef488b92df81","tid":565423,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb9bcb8ee2c9f04089be2ed5da3df934b6b40df","tid":565423,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"有新買新 同埋mx500有5年warranty"},{"pid":"07a39c39aede7d63975add7033680cfd5784101c","tid":565423,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"MX500"},{"pid":"1440be71ff61bfb32ff1e278a793bf22eb0d7e07","tid":565423,"uid":128613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T19:05:36.000Z","msg":"Samsung 860 evo"},{"pid":"7d9eb283e86fe2386c2f0b83a471041f2faca472","tid":565423,"uid":1038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"之前見平，999 入左隻mx300 ，用落無咩問題"},{"pid":"d1669128778c5b0357c0ddc0f69d709f97961fa6","tid":565423,"uid":128613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d9eb283e86fe2386c2f0b83a471041f2faca472","tid":565423,"uid":1038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"之前見平，999 入左隻mx300 ，用落無咩問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"琴日見邪都 都係999 MX300 525GB"},{"pid":"b6831117a58e21a3c07b0e06b02d1bb80c0d307a","tid":565423,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"mx500 速度同耐久度較 mx300 優勝少少，惟供電用料上 mx300 高汁過 mx500。<br />\n<br />\nMX500 優點：<br />\n擁有高達 560/510 MB/s 的循序讀取 / 寫入速度及高達 95K/90K IOPS 的隨機讀取 / 寫入速度，內裡採用 64 層堆疊的 256 GB 元件。而美光的浮閘式 NAND 使用的 CMOS Under the Array (CUA) 架構設計，可使得晶片的占用空間降至最低，達到僅有 59 平方公釐，是全世界最小的 256 GB 晶片，另外提供 5 年有限保固，並可獲得 Crucial Storage Executive 軟體工具的支援，以進行輕鬆的硬碟維護。<br />\n<br />\nmx500 缺點：<br />\n1. 控制晶片由 Marvell 變成 Silicon Motion SM2258<br />\n2. 以往的進階功能 Power Loss Protection 變成 Integrated Power Loss Immunity<br />\n3. 陶瓷電容改圍繞在快閃記憶體周圍，線路設計布局不像以往那樣集中，換言之電容落少咗。"},{"pid":"63b5a4dae1b0119ea98fae7392e31a92ae55dc69","tid":565423,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"MX300 用Marvell主控，供電用料冇偷工減料，惟速度同耐用度慢mx500少少，得3年保。"},{"pid":"b0319068bf5d628669b6f44bf1331b55ac09030d","tid":565423,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"理論設計耐用度部分（TBW），MX500 的 250GB 版耐用提升 25％、500GB 版 12.5％、1TB 並未調整、2TB 大躍進 75％ 之多。"},{"pid":"a4d02027f253cf79d0de66a4d31b3ae20108995a","tid":565423,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"睇完講解<br />\n都係決定買mx500<br />\n多謝大家解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ecda26626de5d5f839a89027c62fcb176c21ac","tid":565423,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a4d02027f253cf79d0de66a4d31b3ae20108995a","tid":565423,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"睇完講解<br />\n都係決定買mx500<br />\n多謝大家解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"較明顯嘅分別係mx300部份型號會多GB過mx500。<br />\n<br />\n2xxGB:<br />\nMX300 275GB ($6xx)<br />\nMX500 250GB ($6xx)<br />\n<br />\n5xxGB:<br />\nMX300 525GB (1k)<br />\nMX500 500GB (1k)<br />\n<br />\n7xxGB:<br />\nMX300 750GB (1.5k)<br />\nMX500 n/a"},{"pid":"9c8f7e856519cf0c68a9eca640911ff5a51f356e","tid":565423,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"年三十買咗mx500<br />\n唔放重要嘢咪試下新嘢囉"}]}